Package ca.mcgill.ecse211.project

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Display
    Display class print out the location of the robot.
    Localization
    The Localization class localizes the robot using the falling edge method.
    Main
    The main Class that will run the program.
    MapRouter
    The MapRouter class store a basic idea of the map.
    Navigation
    Navigation class, most of the action method for this robot is defined here.
    Odometer
    The odometer class keeps track of the robot's (x, y, theta) position.
    OdometerCorrector
    The OdometerCorrector class finds out if it is safe for the robot to move to the next tile, uses the light sensors to correct the odometer.
    Resources
    Integrate this carefully with your existing Resources class.
    Resources.Point
    Represents a coordinate point on the competition map grid.
    Resources.Region
    Represents a region on the competition map grid, delimited by its lower-left and upper-right corners (inclusive).
